reviewText: Fast shipping and kids love the dvd!
This DVD did not come with the informational insert inside (adjacent to the DVD) that was standard with all my other Veggie Tales DVD's.

2 of the stories on this set are my very favorites (and its not madam blueberry)
My nephew got me hooked on them about 30 years. So much in there for the Kids but just as much fun for the adults
You just have listen. Veggie tales rock!!
Great price and my son loves veggies tales!! This was a christmas Gift and he loves them!

After watching this DVD with my grand children, I must state I am surprised at the music played after the movie.
This "rap" type music was more for teens than toddlers. Never dreamed I would have to monitor a Veggie Tale movie
because of the music, which wasn't a part of the movie, it wasn't necessary.
